      • fromArray

        public static Tuple2 fromArray(java.lang.Object[] list)
        Create a Tuple2 with the given array if it is small enough to fit inside a Tuple2 to Tuple8.
        参数:
        list - the content of the Tuple (size 1 to 8)
        返回:
        The new Tuple2.
        抛出:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the array is not of length 1-8
